<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.11">
<l>aṭiyōṅku nūṟṟuvar vīyavaṉ ṟaivark karuḷceyta</l>
<l>neṭiyōṉait teṉkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉkuṟ ṟēvalka</l>
<l>ḷaṭiyārnta vāyirat tuḷḷivai pattavaṉ ṟōṇṭarmēṉ</l>
<l>muṭivārak kaṟkiṟkil caṉmañ ceyyāmai muṭiyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If able to learn up to the end</l>
<l>on his slaves these ten in the thousand filled with [metrical] lines</l>
<l>that are the services of Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr on the Tall one</l>
<l>who did grace to the Five that day so that the Hundred high in origin perished,</l>
	<l>not being [re-]born will be accomplished.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
